Use following commands in your project accordingly in terminal

# Create Django Project
-> pip install Django 
-> django-admin startproject doc_utility [Project Name]
-> python manage.py startapp utilities   [Project App Name]

# Use migration commands 
-> python manage.py makemigrations
-> python manage.py migrate
-> python manage.py showmigrations

# Install libraries before using them
-> pip install python-docx 
-> pip install python-pptx
-> pip install reportlab

# Run server
-> python manage.py runserver 
